        remediation: 'Implement idle timeout (e.g., 15–30 minutes) and absolute session expiry.',
        whyItMatters: 'If a user leaves a device unattended, an unlimited session can allow unauthorized access to PHI.',
        howItHappens: 'Teams use default session settings, long-lived JWTs without rotation, or omit inactivity tracking.',
        properFix: 'Configure server-side sessions with idle and absolute timeouts. For JWTs, use short-lived access tokens + refresh token rotation and revocation.',
